  }} }} 'Rotenone' is an odourless, colourless, crystalline ketonic chemical
  compound used as a broad-spectrum insecticide, piscicide, and pesticide. It
  occurs naturally in the seeds and stems of several plants, such as the jicama
  vine plant; and the roots of several members of Fabaceae.
